title: Aimers (band)
text:
Aimers (Korean: 에이머스) is a South Korean boy band that debuted in 2022 under Hyper Rhythm. The group consists of six members: Seunghyun, Eunjun, Doryun, Yoel, Seunghwan, and Wooyoung.
